Okay, so you know how the Quest system works. TWO more
thing you need to know. How to navigate Menus and Combat!
Pressing with TWO FINGERS will go back in the
LevelUp UI.\|\|
The "Back" Buttons listed on SUB Menus will go back to
the previous menu. "Back" buttons are also on main menus
as well.\|\|
Attacking and Moving are NOT done simultaneously.\|\|
When Attacking, your Character will stop and attack in the
current position. Time your attacks Carefully!
(Semi-Turn based Action)\|\|
Sometimes... it may be wise to retreat\|\|
